  <description>
    Robotiq Vision System Calibration Board for UR5 / UR10.
    17 x 23 chessboard squares, each 14 mm x 14 mm.
    Full board: 258 mm x 392 mm x 3 mm.
    Inner corner pattern (OpenCV): 16 x 22.
    Square size: 0.014 m.
    The frame origin is at the bottom-left corner of the board surface (Z = 0 = top face).
  </description>
